descriptionNullable:
Context
This dataset contains information about Manga and Otaku who watch it. There already is a similar dataset [https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/azathoth42/myanimelist](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/azathoth42/myanimelist) but it anime based while this one is manga based

data was scraped using Jikan api

Content
The dataset contains 4 files:
mal_manga_df.csv contains list of manga, with title, mal_id, type, chapter, volumes, status, rank, author, and serialization
note: some manga have missing chapter/volumes this is either because it ongoing or does not exist

mal_users_manga.csv contains manga id and ranked given by user 

users.csv/users_part2.csv are the users who where used to scrape data
title: Myanimelist dataset containing over 5000 manga
